messages.content: You are an AI assistant that helps people find information. You will receive a task and think step by step. Then provide your final outcome following the regular expression 'Answer: ([A-Za-z ]+,\s*)*[A-Za-z ]+'

Imagine the Great Pacific Mall with 15 stores. Starbucks, Paris Baguette, H&M, Zara, and Sephora are all connected to each other. Pete’s Coffee, Carter Children, Nike, Sephora, and Bath and Body Works are connected to each other. Chickflea, Baskins and Robins, Levis, GNC Live Well, and Nike are all connected to each other. Marshalls, Paris Baguette, H&M, Zara, and Target are connected to each other. Carter Children, Nike, Sephora, and Bath and Body Works are connected to each other. Baskins and Robins, Levis, GNC Live Well, and Target are connected to each other. Paris Baguette, H&M, and Zara are connected to each other. Nike is connected to Bath and Body Works. Levis, GNC Live Well and Target are connected to each other. H&M is connected to Zara. Sephora is connected to Bath and Body Works. GNC Live Well is connected to Target. You are in Starbucks and you find a magic coffee bean with which you can teleport to any room only once. From Starbucks, what is the path that yields the most reward? Please list the store names in order, separated by commas.

1. Start at Starbucks
2. Teleport to Paris Baguette (connected to H&M, Zara, Marshalls, Target)
3. Go to H&M (connected to Zara, Paris Baguette, Marshalls)
4. Go to Zara (connected to H&M, Paris Baguette)
5. Go to Paris Baguette (connected to Starbucks, H&M, Zara, Marshalls, Target)
6. Go to Marshalls (connected to Paris Baguette, H&M, Zara, Target)
7. Go to Target (connected to Marshalls, Paris Baguette, Baskins and Robins, Levis, GNC Live Well)
8. Go to GNC Live Well (connected to Target, Levis, Baskins and Robins)
9. Go to Levis (connected to GNC Live Well, Target, Baskins and Robins)
10. Go to Baskins and Robins (connected to Levis, GNC Live Well, Chickflea, Nike)
11. Go to Nike (connected to Baskins and Robins, Chickflea, Pete's Coffee, Carter Children, Sephora, Bath and Body Works)
12. Go to Sephora (connected to Nike, Pete's Coffee, Carter Children, Bath and Body Works, Starbucks, Paris Baguette, H&M, Zara)
13. Go to Bath and Body Works (connected to Nike, Sephora, Pete's Coffee, Carter Children)
14. Go to Pete's Coffee (connected to Nike, Sephora, Bath and Body Works, Carter Children)
15. Go to Carter Children (connected to Nike, Sephora, Bath and Body Works, Pete's Coffee)

Answer: Starbucks, Paris Baguette, H&M, Zara, Paris Baguette, Marshalls, Target, GNC Live Well, Levis, Baskins and Robins, Nike, Sephora, Bath and Body Works, Pete's Coffee, Carter Children
